After recent and extensive refurbishments to the building,  now is the opportunity to secure your new office space.

*318sqm. Refurbished open plan ground floor space. Please view available floor plan for potential layout.

Refurbishment works have included; installation of new roof and air-conditioning system throughout, installation of lift servicing level 1, upgrade of external features including the facade, tiling and landscaping.

Excellent tenancy signage is available which is highly exposed to passing traffic.

Basement staff parking is available along with ample client and overflow parking on the island.

For further information or to arrange an inspection please contact the agent listed.

Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Opposite the large Bruce Bishop Carpark

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Gateway is a popular 10-storey office building located at the southern end of the Surfers Paradise CBD. The building has recently undergone refurbishments in all common areas and vacant tenancies.

- 94sqm to 117sqm (approximate)
- Exceptional views of the hinterland, river and Surfers Paradise
- Within walking distance to a G:Link tram station, Q1 building, central Surfers Paradise, restaurants and cafes
- Opposite the large Bruce Bishop Carpark
- Security access
- Generous incentives on offer

For more information or to arrange an inspection, contact the agent.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: OUTSTANDING OPPORTUNITIES WITHIN A WELL RECOGNISED BUILDING

Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Close proximity to Bruce Bishop carpark

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
Boutique two-level office building at southern end of Surfers Paradise within close proximity to Bruce Bishop carpark and Surfers Paradise light rail station at the Q1 Building.

There are two suites available which will suit a range of professional service occupiers.  The spaces are presented to a high standard and both have good natural light.

- 112sqm suite: fully fitted to a very high standard, glass partitioning allowing natural light penetration through suite
- 157sqm suite: open plan layout, kitchenette and exclusive use 26sqm balcony overlooking park
- Secure basement parking
- Suit professional service occupiers

For further details contact Tania Moore via the links above.
